lead_paragraph: Militants carried out two attacks in and around Grozny, as the country’s Russian-backed leader projected the appearance of being in control of the situation.

headline.print_headline: Rebels Battle With Police in Chechnya
headline.main: Clashes in Chechen Capital Leave at Least Seven Militants Dead
